sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant GR as GraphRuntimeRunner
    participant G as Graph Engine
    participant PA as PlannerAgent
    participant PE as PlanExecutor
    participant TE as ToolExecutor
    participant OBS as MetricsObserver
    participant DB as SQLite

    U->>API: POST query + session_id
    API->>API: RequestID → trace_id
    API->>GR: GraphService.execute()
    GR->>GR: 创建 AgentState + begin_execution()
    Note over GR,DB: execution_id 生成，Observer 开始录制

    GR->>G: astream(state)

    G->>G: memory_load（加载 short/long/episodic memory）
    G->>PA: planner_node → create_plan(query)
    PA-->>G: Plan（3 steps: weather→map→budget）
    G->>G: compile_plan（PlanGraphCompiler → 子图）
    G->>G: router_node（绑定 tool_hint / ToolRouter）
    G->>PE: execution_node → 执行子图 step_1..N
    PE->>TE: weather / map / budget
    TE-->>PE: tool outputs → global_context
    PE-->>G: execution_trace 更新

    G->>G: memory_persist（写入 episodic memory）
    G->>G: critic_node（评估是否满足 goal）
    alt need_replan = false
        G->>G: finalize → should_stop=true
    else need_replan = true
        G->>G: replanner → router → execution（循环）
    end

    loop 每个 graph / tool 事件
        G-->>OBS: on_graph_event
        G-->>DB: ExecutionRecorder（异步队列）
        TE-->>OBS: on_tool_record
        TE-->>DB: tool_calls 写入
    end

    G-->>GR: final AgentState
    GR-->>API: GraphExecuteResponse
    API-->>U: JSON 或 SSE stream（start→graph_node→done）
